dungeon.Dungeon

public abstract class Dungeon
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Room>, java.lang.Cloneable
A Dungeon is a 3 dimension matrix of tiles. Implements the Prototype design pattern and is built by a builder class.
